@startuml sequence-complete-task
actor Employee
participant "React SPA" as Web
participant "FastAPI" as API
database PostgreSQL as DB

Employee -> Web: outcome + comment
Web -> API: POST /tasks/{id}/complete
API -> API: verify JWT, role, assignee
API -> DB: UPDATE task status\nINSERT completion
DB --> API: ok
API --> Web: TaskResponse
Web --> Employee: updated card
@enduml
